Minecraft 1.14 Village & Pillage Update Videos ► https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7VmhWGNRxKixIX8tWEQn-BnYKE9AaAXk
Minecraft 1.14 snapshot 18w45a introduced scaffolding! A new block to replace dirt as temporary scaffolding. We also get to see Illager raids for the first time and signs are now editable!
